{"tid":1128536,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Don Cheadle 談及收到Marvel 邀請飾演War Machine","createTime":"2019-04-28T01:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T01:40:15.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47224e5ff952d24408655a4f34808d072ebe5678","tid":1128536,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:05:24.000Z","msg":"Don Cheadle 表示Marvel 當時只給予他一小時去決定要否加入成為Avengers 一員，壓力相當大吧？更甚的是，他當時正身處女兒的生日派對中。<br />\n<br />\nDon 當時正在為女兒慶祝生日，RDJ 和Kevin Feige 分別致電告訴他，Terrence Howard 不會回歸飾演War Machine，然後有一個小時的時間讓他去考慮是否想要取代Terrence Howard。「你要放手一搏，相信我們」Don 回憶兩人對他說這句話。但如果我決定加盟的話，我們談論的是十年甚至是十二年的承諾，然後我向他們說，我正在女兒的生日派對中，於是他們回覆「噢，那麼給你兩小時吧」。<br />\n<br />\n巧合的是，Don 在第二日就遇見Terrence，他表示「我們從來沒有甚麼過節和矛盾」。兩人認識對方多年，更曾經合作拍攝奧斯卡最佳電影《Crash》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2019%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fdon-cheadle-replacing-terrence-howard-avengers-endgame-1203198923%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fl.facebook.com%2Fl.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fvariety.com%252F2019%252Ffilm%252Fnews%252Fdon-cheadle-replacing-terrence-howard-avengers-endgame-1203198923%252F&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8q%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=d8ea5670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2019%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fdon-cheadle-replacing-terrence-howard-avengers-endgame-1203198923%2F</a>"},{"pid":"b77c7d4eb0c2b64ec470c402a148fd34516925ea","tid":1128536,"uid":236891,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:08:35.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得next time baby先真係似tony老友<br />\n我而家都未接受到captain planet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\na4重夠膽話自己超級英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係tony整甲比佢只會係一個普通軍人<br />\n<br />\n佢教識人要同d勁人做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6400f536c15e97aad36730d5fe8f93fd7b8ebbc","tid":1128536,"u